Package: creaemission
Type: Package
Title: CREA Emission Portal - Emissions Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("CREA", "Hubert Thieriot", email = "hubert@energyandcleanair.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package and Shiny portal for analyzing and visualizing emissions data from multiple sources (CEDS, EDGAR), with support for both national and provincial-level analysis, interactive charts, and mapping capabilities.
